data.description: This stunning property offers a covered patio with a greenbelt behind the property, perfect for relaxing and entertaining outdoors. Cozy up by the fireplace in the family room during cooler evenings. The upgraded landscaping adds a touch of elegance to the exterior, creating a warm and inviting curb appeal. This single-story gem is in pristine condition, ensuring a modern and comfortable living experience. Located just off the Chisholm Trail Parkway, this home offers easy access to a plethora of shopping centers, including shops off of McPherson Rd, Overton Ridge, and Clearfork. You'll also appreciate the proximity to Tarleton State University in Fort Worth for higher educational opportunities. For families, the property is situated within walking distance of highly-rated schools, making the morning commute a breeze. Moreover, you'll have the convenience of HEB, just a short 15-minute drive away. Seller willing to provide $5,000 in seller paid concessions towards a rate buy down.
